{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dbiir/UER-py/issues/334","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dbiir/UER-py","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dbiir/UER-py/issues/334/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dbiir/UER-py/issues/334/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dbiir/UER-py/issues/334/events","html_url":"https://github.com/dbiir/UER-py/issues/334","id":1320341945,"node_id":"I_kwDOCsNQKM5OstG5","number":334,"title":"finetune/run_classifier.py 关于文本对训练中seg的赋值","user":{"login":"husheng-liu","id":62696645,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYyNjk2NjQ1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/62696645?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu","html_url":"https://github.com/husheng-liu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2022-07-28T03:27:29Z","updated_at":"2022-07-29T10:16:08Z","closed_at":"2022-07-29T10:16:08Z","author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"源代码\r\n                src_b = args.tokenizer.convert_tokens_to_ids(args.tokenizer.tokenize(text_b) + [SEP_TOKEN])\r\n                src = src_a + src_b\r\n                seg = [1] * len(src_a) + [2] * len(src_b)\r\nseg 一般认为是用于区分text_a和text_b,但是一般是0 和 1 ，不知道1 和2在输入bert 或者transformer的embedding是否可行。\r\n如果可行的情况下，那么这种写法应该会使得该项目在与hugging face 的Transformer 的分词或者Tokenizer 分词略有不同，是否应该提醒用户需要注意？\r\n\r\n\r\nclass WordPosSegEmbedding(WordPosEmbedding):\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    BERT embedding consists of three parts:\r\n    word embedding, position embedding, and segment embedding.\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    def __init__(self, args, vocab_size):\r\n        super(WordPosSegEmbedding, self).__init__(args, vocab_size)\r\n        self.segment_embedding = nn.Embedding(3, args.emb_size)\r\n另外这一块的写法中，nn.Embedding参数设为3，虽然可以，但是理论上将2似乎更加符合seg的输入，因为seg 一般只有0 和1\r\n以上仅作探讨，盼复~+","closed_by":{"login":"husheng-liu","id":62696645,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYyNjk2NjQ1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/62696645?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu","html_url":"https://github.com/husheng-liu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/husheng-liu/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dbiir/UER-py/issues/334/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dbiir/UER-py/issues/334/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}